  "content": "<p data-pid=\"BXaaSZKl\">在追求理性的过程中，我们会遇到许多有趣而深刻的新想法。通常，这也意味着结识志同道合的朋友，加入能激励自我提升的群体。但<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Death-Spirals-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《死亡螺旋》</a>系列指出，团结在共同利益和闪亮理念下的群体，也可能受到某些危害的影响。要从理性主义社区中获得最大收益，我们必须克服这些危害。</p><p data-pid=\"KfxvJg1f\">——<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Rationality-An-Introduction\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">《理性：序言》</a><sup data-text=\"理性：序言\" data-url=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/827867654\" data-draft-node=\"inline\" data-draft-type=\"reference\" data-numero=\"1\">[1]</sup>by Rob Bensinger</p><hr/><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1948679023468213696\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"情感启发式\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-95662db86354d22871110f330efa63d2.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">情感启发式</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1949761528619316687\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"可评估性（与假期购物省钱技巧）\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-59315637f9ec97e747f93b98b1b2632e.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">可评估性（与假期购物省钱技巧）</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1951935719577739806\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"无界标度、陪审团巨额裁决与未来预言\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9175bc30642c38f0cb904b1bc37f51bc.webp?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">无界标度、陪审团巨额裁决与未来预言</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1953391609371686423\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"晕轮效应\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c0979e66c2bed97937290a1ec0a58b35.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">晕轮效应</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1955423601445545825\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"超级英雄偏见\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-92634dc8fae2d75548f7291e7a763394.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">超级英雄偏见</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1959907024906220896\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"蛐蛐救世主\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-f26dd73c6e51e9d97c07add96c2dd627.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">蛐蛐救世主</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1961358134401564985\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"情感死亡螺旋\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-0697693c731bf6b3323770dad6def1c7.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">情感死亡螺旋</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1971146192453886749\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"抵制快乐死亡螺旋\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-a531f71cd78082d5f92a7cd9b8a549f4.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">抵制快乐死亡螺旋</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1972605380472334329\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"不加批判的超临界状态\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-a3b790ca942cfdcc42de7cf558fd16ad.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">不加批判的超临界状态</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1976228566535525563\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"群体信念的蒸发冷却\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6b1098b0123ed1c46a66235f36706044.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">群体信念的蒸发冷却</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1978053267981349691\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"当无人敢于呼吁克制\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b9cfacd87752c7f22daada12af151c95.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">当无人敢于呼吁克制</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1982503482440320981\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"罗伯斯山洞实验\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-6dc98f6cfe0d52e01fba371b0d61d110.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">罗伯斯山洞实验</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1998695537822683388\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"任何主义都想自立为教\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-25912aa7380066c56997712e42ae8593.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">任何主义都想自立为教</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1993332131317970026\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"真理的卫道士\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-0ca0069b408c936b0bf7317d3a5be209.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">真理的卫道士</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1993332714330399105\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"基因池的卫道士\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-201fc55b48828c78c81b93fa01414d1e.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">基因池的卫道士</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1994481037204553840\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"安·兰德的卫道士\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-984b9f573b1d7eb812f3dd6455570f2b.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">安·兰德的卫道士</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1996321798212585333\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"两则关于「邪教」的公案\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-229f780e0c05ae22605e0c3e9a0a02bb.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">两则关于「邪教」的公案</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1996695383045317323\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"Asch 的从众实验\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-9390141af8ddf59228a1be8719d7535b.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">Asch 的从众实验</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1997250859650807189\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"论表达顾虑\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/v2-b2ae91f26fce08afa54a08f7168f5db6.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">论表达顾虑</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1999056337015940656\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"孤勇的反抗\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-ec2637930139ee16fb66ef934a3e110c.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">孤勇的反抗</a><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/2004256642078884961\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"邪教式反邪\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c6fac434f0631948311ca23a08f2b237.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">邪教式反邪</a><hr/><p data-pid=\"FBW3KE6_\">上一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1946143276831859011\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"起源谬误\" data-draft-cover=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-2d32595d85f958901cf6582bf1381d70.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">起源谬误</a><p data-pid=\"8YXENe3d\">下一篇：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/1948679023468213696\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-draft-title=\"情感启发式\" data-draft-cover=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-95662db86354d22871110f330efa63d2.jpg?source=7e7ef6e2&amp;needBackground=1\" class=\"internal\">情感启发式</a><hr/><blockquote data-pid=\"ep3Me-D_\"><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=http%3A//paratranz.cn/projects/3131\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Thoughts Memo</a> 汉化组译制<br/>感谢主要译者 claude-3-opus，校对 <span class=\"nolink\">Jarrett Ye</span><br/>原文：<a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.readthesequences.com/Death-Spirals-Sequence\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">Death Spirals - Sequence</a></blockquote>",
